{"tid":2437484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紫荊黨主席李山：成員爭取參與立法會及政府執政團隊等","createTime":"2021-03-08T01:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T04:04:40.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"076ac5abe122095e47689d12d6faab5584bee25e","tid":2437484,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T01:56:29.000Z","msg":"全國政協委員、新成立的紫荊黨黨主席李山指，紫荊黨的成員將會爭取參與立法會、特首選委會及政府執政團隊等政治架構，形容紫荊黨的顏色就是「愛國」，與其他建制派政黨目標一致，是同路軍。<br />\n<br />\n紫荊黨成立一年，李山在北京接受本台專訪時表示，反修例風波演變成暴亂，所以與志同道合的朋友成立愛國愛港的政黨，共有13名創黨成員，雖然他們大部分都是海外留學，但並非「新港人黨」、「海歸黨」，強調是為香港服務，不止是維護一國兩制50年不變，更要力爭「百年不變」。<br />\n<br />\n李山又表示，自己並非共產黨員，至於他本人會否參與下屆立法會，李山指，一切皆有可能，但現時會集中建立黨的基礎，對黨或是個人而言，參選立法會都不是重點考慮的方向。<br />\n<br />\n在內地出生的李山，畢業於清華大學，到海外留學後，回港定居20多年。他表示，雖然不懂廣東話，但並無妨礙對香港人服務，現在會開始學習廣東話，以增加與港人的交流。"},{"pid":"1328215d464c5fd4dd913ead9a321beb1f215eed","tid":2437484,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T01:56:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579313-20210308.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579313-20210308.htm&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058tHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=841f0b75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579313-20210308.htm&h=317f4a08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579313-20210308.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a72b09afbb03ad1ee38a7046872c0f2afbb4cc59","tid":2437484,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T01:57:18.000Z","msg":"你喜歡啦"},{"pid":"bcf9bff6292edfddc1399fdf5868faf259be9519","tid":2437484,"uid":323449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T01:58:25.000Z","msg":"X你XX !"},{"pid":"154f2fc5852d7f7c1e1c40bd480bfe07558350cc","tid":2437484,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"你都死撚咗啦百年不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n共產黨講嘢有撚誠信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ab859351976c019805d51777e6f8eefcc35174","tid":2437484,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d688693127cea4f490b8072d49f6e164d74b38c4","tid":2437484,"uid":301406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:04:40.000Z","msg":"往後十年就要睇住依條仆街指指點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}